gov.nih.nlm.meme.client
Class EditingClient

java.lang.Object
  gov.nih.nlm.meme.client.ClientAPI
      gov.nih.nlm.meme.client.EditingClient
public class EditingClient
extends ClientAPI

This client is a super-client that combines the functionality of a number other clients including:

  • ActionClient
  • AuxiliaryDataClient
  • CoreDataClient
  • FinderClient
  • WorklistClient
This client API is intended to have enough functionality to fully support an interactive editing environment. Each editing session will make use of a single EditingClient which creates and manages all of the necessary Authentication and session issues that the server requires. With the properties properly configured, accessing auxiliary data services is as simple as instantiating class and calling its methods. There are only a small number of methods that are managed directly by this class, all others are forwarded to private instances of the sub-APIs.

Author:
MEME Group
